00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:58.399
and I've been authorized to come down

00:08:58.399 --> 00:09:01.399
and go through it in a thorough manner.

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:04.399
So this is payback for turning down my father's offer

00:09:04.399 --> 00:09:06.399
to join him in Metropolis.

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:10.399
Lionel has been very tolerant of your excesses.

00:09:10.399 --> 00:09:13.399
But this time you didn't spend the money

00:09:13.399 --> 00:09:15.399
on parties and sports cars.

00:09:15.399 --> 00:09:17.399
And he wants to know where it went.

00:09:18.399 --> 00:09:22.399
Do you know what my father gave me for my 10th birthday?

00:09:22.399 --> 00:09:24.399
A copy of The Will to Power.

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.399
Behold the Superman.

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:30.399
Man is something to be overcome.

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:34.399
Sun Tzu, Machiavelli, Nietzsche.

00:09:34.399 --> 00:09:38.399
They were the voices that nurtured me after my mother died.

00:09:38.399 --> 00:09:40.399
My father made every question a quiz,

00:09:40.399 --> 00:09:42.399
every choice a test.

00:09:42.399 --> 00:09:44.399
Second best was for losers,

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:46.399
