00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:48.399
Those were the lessons I grew up with.

00:09:48.399 --> 00:09:50.399
I'll remember that if I'm ever interviewed

00:09:50.399 --> 00:09:52.399
by the Biography Channel.

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:54.399
All I'm saying, Dominic,

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:57.399
is try and remember who I was raised by.

00:09:57.399 --> 00:10:00.399
I try to deny it, but I'm still my father's son.

00:10:01.399 --> 00:10:03.399
Tread carefully.

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:08.399
Here you go.

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:16.399
