00:10:20.399 --> 00:10:22.399
My father and I are going to the sea.

00:10:22.399 --> 00:10:24.399
Of course you do.

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:26.399
My father and I went on a fishing trip once.

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:28.399
