00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:10.399
Well, there was an incident involving your son

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:12.399
and Lex's Porsche

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:14.399
and a bridge.

00:12:14.399 --> 00:12:16.399
Lex has spent a considerable amount of time

00:12:16.399 --> 00:12:18.399
and capital researching the crash

00:12:18.399 --> 00:12:20.399
and I was wondering if you knew why.

00:12:20.399 --> 00:12:22.399
Look, the truth is, Lex's Porsche

00:12:22.399 --> 00:12:24.399
