00:12:24.399 --> 00:12:26.399
His car went off the bridge into the water.

00:12:26.399 --> 00:12:28.399
My son jumped in, risked his life to save him.

00:12:28.399 --> 00:12:30.399
That's the end of the story.

00:12:30.399 --> 00:12:32.399
And you wouldn't know why he commissioned

00:12:32.399 --> 00:12:34.399
