00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:24.399
Oh.

00:13:26.399 --> 00:13:28.399
Where is Whitney?

00:13:28.399 --> 00:13:30.399
I don't know. His mom said he'd be here.

00:13:40.399 --> 00:13:42.399
Clark!

00:13:42.399 --> 00:13:44.399
How's Whitney's dad?

00:13:46.399 --> 00:13:48.399
